lead_paragraph: Adam Duvall's two-run single was all Cincinnati needed as the Reds beat the St. Louis Cardinals 2-1 on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Duvall's Single Lifts Reds to 2-1 Win Over Cardinals
